title: Santa Cruz: Paradise Lost
description: Congrats to Santa Cruz for winning Transworld's Skate and Create! Check out the video at skateboarding.com. They filmed so much they had enough extras to make this bonus part for Strange Notes. Featuring Jason Jessee, Emmanuel Guzman, Sid Melvin, Strubing, Hosoi and more!
